{"word":"G396 - ἀνατρέπω - anatrépō - an-at-rep'-o - Overthrow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνατρέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anatrépō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-at-rep'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Overthrow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவிழ்த்துப்போடு"},{"paragraph":"to overthrow, overturn, destroy, ethically, to subvert"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5157 - τροπή - tropḗ - trop-ay'/5157\">G5157</a>; to <i>overturn</i> (figuratively): - overthrow, subvert.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}